{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_02_02_01",
  "title": "STAGE2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりスリクスがライブを……？\nこれは一体……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suddenly IIIX is doing a live…?\nWhat on earth…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4657140732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……やることはやりました\nでは、失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We did what we had to do.\nWell then‚ excuse us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666666667,
      "endTime": 9.6979138534,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1055.8367092000012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.9000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaも早くSNSに投稿しよーっと\nてかfran、これでバズらなかったら覚えてろよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to post this on SNS right away!\nBy the way fran‚ if this doesn't go viral‚ remember that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9000000001,
      "endTime": 18.5041043282,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4027.918354599999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.5666667939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "私も好きでやってる訳じゃないわよ……\nはぁ……とりあえず、次お願いしまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not doing this because I like it…\nSigh… Anyway‚ on to the next request.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5666667939,
      "endTime": 30.2000002544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2500002544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "行ってしまった……\n説明くらいしてほしかったんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They've gone…\nI wish they had explained…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3000002544,
      "endTime": 37.5312918346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.7333335877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "よく分かりませんけど、こんな貸し切り状態で\nスリクスのライブが観れるなんて感動ですー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't really understand‚ but being able to see IIIX's live\nin this exclusive setting is so moving!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7333335877,
      "endTime": 44.6967123033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9000002544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ？\n今度は別のグループが出て来ましたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nNow another group is coming out!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9000002544,
      "endTime": 48.995850531399995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 266.6666666000026
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.333078900005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーん！　さとみさーん！\n楽しんでますか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Satomi-san!\nAre you enjoying yourselves~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1000017803,
      "endTime": 56.1707732836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私達――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3666689555,
      "endTime": 57.666667175200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0827904145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0827904145,
      "endTime": 59.6827906687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0585523066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ここからは、うちらトリエルが\nもっともっと盛り上げていくで～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From here on out‚ TRINITYAiLE is\ngoing to hype things up even more~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0585523066,
      "endTime": 65.1333338419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.3959858974
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　でもその前に、説明が先かな？\nスリクスさん達、しないまま引っ込んじゃったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! But before that‚ shouldn't we explain?\nIIIX just left without saying anything",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3959858974,
      "endTime": 73.2000948032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.395990475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。{user}さん、さとみさん\n驚かせてしまってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. {user}-san‚ Satomi-san\nWe're sorry for surprising you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.395990475,
      "endTime": 79.9666717528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.3293156703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "このライブは、星見プロのアイドル達が\nお二人に、日頃の感謝を伝えるために企画した――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This live was a special live for today only\nto express our gratitude to you two",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3293156703,
      "endTime": 87.52932253670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7959843715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "一日限りのスペシャルライブです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "planned by the idols of Hoshimi Prods!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7959843715,
      "endTime": 90.0626558701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.2959691126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "今日はありったけの想いを込めて\nお二人のために歌います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll sing today with\nall our hearts for you two!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2959691126,
      "endTime": 94.7626558701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちらからの、サプライズプレゼントです\nほんまにいつも、ありがとうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a surprise present from us\nThank you so much for always being there",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9626413743,
      "endTime": 101.3021478097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9647060792
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.3647246439
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "み、みなさんが、私達のため、だけに……\nしぇんぱい……これ、夢じゃないですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "E-Everyone is doing this just for us…\nSenpai… This isn't a dream‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4313854616,
      "endTime": 114.1022922914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6313913106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、驚いたな……\n俺達に秘密でこんなライブを計画していたなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I'm surprised…\nPlanning a live like this in secret for us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2980521282,
      "endTime": 120.6802741131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.2980521282
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8647187949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なら、さっきのスリクスのライブも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Then‚ the IIIX's live earlier was though…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8647187949,
      "endTime": 124.0246054412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1313913106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "それでは聴いて下さい。私達の、想いを込めた一曲を\n――『réaliser』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then please listen. Our song filled with our hearts\n――『réaliser』",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1647045534,
      "endTime": 133.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.1980523825
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
